Moustache (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moustache_(actor) 0 François-Alexandre Galepides, known by the stage name Moustache, was a French actor and jazz drummer of Greek descent. He was born 14 February 1929 in Paris and died 25 March 1987 in Arpajon in a car accident.
